<br>
I used to play without a monk, enchanter or bard in my group, and we had to evac out of dungeons relatively often :O . It was convenient to succor out to Lavastorm if you were in Sol B, South Ro if you were in Lower Guk, and Butcherblock if you were in Kedge Keep. <br>
